{"type":"message","id":"9cc8f4c6","parentId":"852c9566","timestamp":"2026-04-08T23:42:22.657Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:f61eec2a-69ea-4fd2-84b7-3d424eaaa653 每日推送claudecode最热动态] 请帮我获取最新claudecode相关的最热动态，包括github热门项目、最新工具发布、相关新闻资讯，整理成清晰的内容推送给用户ou_c1435b3d813e202c2f8dda9e6cf0de25\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 9th, 2026 — 7:42 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-08 23:42 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775691742647}}
{"type":"message","id":"dfbaf3ec","parentId":"9cc8f4c6","timestamp":"2026-04-08T23:42:27.771Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户现在需要我获取最新claudecode相关的最热动态，包括github热门项目、最新工具发布、相关新闻资讯，然后整理推送给用户。首先，我需要使用miaoda-web-search技能来搜索相关信息，所以先调用这个工具。根据skill的说明，当需要搜索网页信息时，应该使用miaoda-web-search，所以先读取这个skill的文档，看看怎么使用。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_msrkmhvw00thx6upg267o244","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":31160,"output":133,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31293,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775691742650}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d800b31","parentId":"dfbaf3ec","timestamp":"2026-04-08T23:42:27.810Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_msrkmhvw00thx6upg267o244","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775691747806}}
